**Describe the bug**
impure expression in each block causes infinite loop in runtime

**Severity**
low priority

**To Reproduce**
[repl](https://svelte.dev/repl/132fec6757c94430beb3de6d4d4067ee?version=3.32.3) - uncomment `//state[key] = val;` to crash the browser tab

```svelte
