parse the expression and look for assignments to non-local variables ([sample code](https://stackoverflow.com/a/66372081/10440128))

this would at least detect the simple case shown above.
its harder to detect impure functions, that write to the global state

2\. runtime

in the dev mode runtime, detect the infinite loop, stop it, and help to analyze (start devtools debugger?)

