</div>
```
```ts
p(ctx, [dirty]) {
	if (dirty & /*o*/ 1) {
		toggle_class(div, "test", /*o*/ ctx[0].v);
	}
}
```
https://svelte.dev/repl/5b14ec60637b43a184460475790105c0?version=3.31.2

Given that `<div>{o.v}</div>` does not generate update code, neither should the class directive
