Derived stores only take input from stores they are derived from
In other words derived stores are readonly and you can only bind values to writable ones
Here's a workaround for your use case

```svelte
{#each $things as cb}
	{#if cb.display}
		<label><input type="checkbox" bind:checked={cb.selected} /> Checkbox</label>
	{/if}
{/each}
```

